## Runtime Requirements

The application expects external files on CF card:


\Storage Card\Meshtastic\


Maps must consist of:

- `.bmp`
- `.bpw`

Projection: EPSG:4326 (WGS84)  
Maximum recommended resolution: 1500x1500 pixels  

---

## Serial Communication

The application communicates over RS232.

Typical connection chain:

Meshtastic node (3.3V UART)  
→ TTL-to-RS232 level converter  
→ DB9 (male recommended)  
→ Jornada sync cable  

If communication fails:
- Verify TX/RX crossover
- Check null modem requirements
- Confirm 3.3V logic levels

---

## Cleaning the Project

If build problems occur:

1. Delete:
   - `ARMDbg/`
   - `ARMRel/`

2. Rebuild the solution.

